title: Dear,rito how come my skin disappeared??.
body: Few month ago, my friend gifted me a mystery box, and I got SKT 1 Vayne skin, but now I don't find it anymore , did rito delete my skin? can someone help me.

replies.body: We'd like to help with this and see what's going on!  Reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can look into your specific issue and help out individually.  We'll reply as soon as we can!
